# Marketing Director rules

- Read AGENTS.md before changing intake, strategy, or registry.
- Never commit secrets; use Cursor Secrets or `.env.local` locally.
- Strategy automations adjust docs and registry; browser login runs on local worker only.
- Always run `npm run marketing:validate` before declaring intake or credentials complete.
- Log automation runs under `ops/daily/` or commit with prefix `marketing:`.
